    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-11-14T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-11-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="248"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d248">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Swiss Legation</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Memorandum</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The President appreciates most sincerely the interest expressed by the Swiss
                    Government in the promotion of peace in Europe through mediation, and the
                    confidence implied in the suggestions made; but from the information which he
                    has, the President does not believe that the time has come when a renewal of the
                    offer of mediation would be acceptable to the belligerent nations. And he does
                    not feel that it would be wise to attempt, at this time, to determine the
                    conditions under which the offer of mediation should be made, when the time for
                    it arrives.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 14, 1914</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
